Description: Salmon Evolution ASA is a Norway-based salmon farming company with its production facility under construction on Indre Haroy. The Company emphasizes rational operation, fish welfare and minimal impact on the environment. With use of small amounts of fresh seawater the Company creates optimum production and environmental conditions, improved growth and a shorter production time.
